headline: Blue Owl Capital: Strong Brand Name, Bright Future

headline: TD Cowen Maintains Buy Rating on Franklin Resources (BEN), Keeps $27 PT
summary: On June 5, William Katz from TD Cowen maintained a Buy rating on Franklin Resources, Inc. (NYSE:BEN) and kept the price target unchanged at $27.
